(79, '\r\n                    [五一]&lt;桂林-阳朔-兴坪漓江-象鼻山-世外桃源-蝴蝶泉-银子岩4日游&gt;自选火车/高铁票 20元背景 隔岸观象 戏梦山水间 伴手礼       ', 1260, 'http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/8B/EF/Cii-slqooEaIF_7CABOzSnd9BncAAEO7gAZZKUAE7Ni485_w160_h90_c1_t0.jpg', '<div class="section-box-title">\n                <h3>产品概要</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class="section-box-content">\n                <div class="detail-feature-brief">\n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            行程天数：<strong>4天3晚</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            成团地点：<strong>桂林成团</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            目的地：<strong>桂林</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            往返交通：<strong>火车/火车</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            报名截止时间：<strong>团期前1天18点</strong>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            组团形式：\n                            <strong>\n                                \n                                    \n                                        联合发团；本产品与其他旅行社联合发团。\n                                    \n                                \n                            </strong>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        \n        <div class="section-box-title">\n            <h3>产品特色</h3>\n        </div>\n        \n            \n                \n                \n                    <div class="section-box-content">\n                        \n                            <strong>2017途牛——最佳质量奖！！</strong><br>\n</div>\n                \n                \n                    \n                    \n                        \n                        \n                            <div class="detail-feature-photos">\n                                \n                                <div class="detail-feature-photo detail-feature-photo-1">\n                                    \n                                        <div class="detail-feature-photo-item">\n                                            <div class="detail-feature-photo-item-inner">\n                                                \n                                                    <img src="//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/48/E9/Cii-s1poUkKIJFg2AAgwVvNCIjcAACyawHBUakACDBu849_w1024_h0_c0_t0.jpg">\n</div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    \n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        \n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                \n                    <div class="section-box-content">\n                        \n                            <strong>产品特色</strong><br><font color="#ff9703" style="line-height: 24px; widows: 1;"> ————【错峰出游，豪礼送送送】 ————</font><br>1、3月15日-4月15日班期下单的贵客，<font color="#ff9703">凡参团游客赠送价值10万旅行意外伤害保险</font>，让您的出行更有保障.<br>2、全年感恩回馈，<font color="#ff9703">任何班期出游的贵客每人1份暖心伴手礼桂花糕</font>---感受浓浓桂林情！<br>3、全年感恩回馈，<font color="#ff9703">任何班期出游的贵客均赠送桂林自产【漓江矿泉水】</font>每天一瓶。<br>4、全年感恩回馈，<font color="#ff9703">任何班期出游的贵客均赠送价值198元的山水间演出门票</font>，先到先得！<br>❤❤不得不选择我们的N大理由❤❤<br><font color="#ff9703">【舌尖桂林】</font><font color="#666666">特色餐云集（60