(124, '\r\n                    &lt;重庆-长江三峡-宜昌4日游&gt;重庆进宜昌出，含往返接站服务，赏全景三峡                    ', 2389, 'http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/14/18/Cii9EFbWYUKINfSzABBJkNHo4OcAACcOQHrpl4AEEmo544_w160_h90_c1_t0.jpg', '<div class="section-box-title">\n                <h3>产品概要</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class="section-box-content">\n                <div class="detail-feature-brief">\n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            行程天数：<strong>4天3晚</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            成团地点：<strong>重庆成团</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            目的地：<strong>宜昌</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            往返交通：<strong>自行安排/自行安排</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            报名截止时间：<strong>团期前1天16点</strong>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            组团形式：\n                            <strong>\n                                \n                                    \n                                        联合发团；本产品与其他旅行社联合发团。\n                                        \n                                        根据发团需要，本产品在部分行程段发生团友的变化，请您谅解。拼团次数约为1次，具体次数及行程段视线路收客情况而定。\n                                    \n                                \n                            </strong>\n                        </div>\n\n 