tion-box-title">\n            <h3>产品特色</h3>\n        </div>\n        \n            \n                \n                \n                    <div class="section-box-content">\n                        \n                            <strong>2017途牛——最佳质量奖！！</strong><br><br>\n</div>\n                \n                \n                    \n                    \n                        \n                        \n                            <div class="detail-feature-photos">\n                                \n                                \n                                \n                                <div class="detail-feature-photo detail-feature-photo-1">\n                                    \n                                        <div class="detail-feature-photo-item">\n                                            <div class="detail-feature-photo-item-inner">\n                                                \n                                                    <img src="//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/48/E9/Cii-s1poUkKIJFg2AAgwVvNCIjcAACyawHBUakACDBu849_w1024_h0_c0_t0.jpg">\n</div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    \n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        \n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                \n                    <div class="section-box-content">\n                        \n                            <strong>我们的实力</strong><br>\n                        \n                        【实力品牌】<font color="#ff9703">20年以上</font>旅游接待经验，年度接待全国各地游客<font color="#ff9703">近60万人次</font>，途牛月接待量<font color="#ff9703">突破10000人线</font>，造就桂林旅游电商行业新标杆。<br>【价格实惠】企业实力雄厚，<font color="#ff9703">拥有自营景区、车队，餐厅等多种旅游资源</font>，同时针对高端酒店实行年度包房，让利游客，让广大衣食父母以平民消费，享受至尊待遇！<br>【质量保障】企业实行集团化严格管理，对所有游客<font color="#ff9703">提供售前、售中、售后24小时一对一全天候管家式服务</font>，第一时间为您的出行排忧解难，