606e5787bcf2a1b5a6ff_w1024_h0_c0_t0.jpg">\n</div>\n                                            </div>\n                                        \n                                    \n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        \n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                \n                    <div class="section-box-content">\n                        \n                            <strong>壶口瀑布</strong><br>\n                        \n                        ✿壶口瀑布是中国黄河上的著名瀑布，其奔腾汹涌的气势是中华民族精神的象征。<br>✿黄河至此，两岸石壁峭立，河口收束狭如壶口，故名壶口瀑布。瀑布落差9米，蕴藏丰富的水力资源。 <br>✿车载WIFI随时上网，分享不延误！没事晒晒美照，欢乐无限多。（部分新车未安装完成，特殊路段信号不好如有链接不上敬请谅解！）<br>✿全面提升舒适度，更有每车10%的空座率（节假日、7月-8月暑期不适用请知晓）；\n                    </div>\n                \n                \n                    \n                    \n                        \n                        \n                            <div class="detail-feature-photos">\n                                \n                                <div class="detail-feature-photo detail-feature-photo-1 detail-feature-photo-multi">\n                                    \n                                        \n                                            <div class="detail-feature-photo-item">\n                                                <div class="detail-feature-photo-item-inner">\n                                                    \n                                                        <img src="//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/C4/F3/Cii-T1gLHWeIaDWPAAkmbCUUkHoAADn8QBYZ9kACSaE814_w1024_h0_c0_t0.jpg">\n</div>\n                                            </div>\n                                        \n                                            <div class="detail-feature-photo-item">\n                                                <div class="detail-feature-photo-item-inner">\n                    