(268, '\r\n                    &lt;桂林阳朔-竹筏漓江-聚龙潭-图腾古道-十里画廊-遇龙河-西街3日游&gt;桂林印象 漓江风情、啤酒鱼特色宴、升级2晚近西街酒店           ', 338, 'http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/olb/d2/f4/d2f49014837dbba6ce94aada6672eafc_w160_h90_c1_t0.jpg', '<div class="section-box-title">\n                <h3>产品概要</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class="section-box-content">\n                <div class="detail-feature-brief">\n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            行程天数：<strong>3天2晚</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            成团地点：<strong>广州成团</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            目的地：<strong>桂林</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            往返交通：<strong>汽车/汽车</strong>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            报名截止时间：<strong>团期前1天22点</strong>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    \n                    \n                        <div class="detail-feature-brief-item">\n                            组团形式：\n                            <strong>\n                                \n                                    \n                                        联合发团；本产品与其他旅行社联合发团。\n                                    \n                                \n                            </strong>\n                        </div>\n\n                        \n\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        \n        <div class="section-box-title">\n            <h3>产品特色</h3>\n        </div>\n        \n            \n                \n                \n                    <div class="section-box-content">\n                        \n                            <strong>特色一：阳朔精粹景点</strong><br><font color="#ff9703">1.</font>兴坪漓江-20元人民币毕竟拍摄地，美国克林顿总统之旅，探究兴坪漓江为何令人神往<br><font color="#ff9703">2.</font>竹筏漓江-阳朔必去景点，小竹排江中游，巍巍青山两岸走，很休闲惬意的游览方式<br><font color="#ff9703">3.</font>十里画廊-沿路风景秀丽，如诗如画，仅十里的长度就能让人流连忘返，沉醉其中<br><font color="#ff9703">4.</font>图腾古道-向人民展示远古野人的生活状态，可与狂野的甄皮岩人对歌、起舞，疯狂<br><font color="#ff9703">5.</font>金 水 岩-阳朔大、有特色、令人开心刺激而且是世界闻名的地下河水晶岩洞<br><font color="#ff9703">6.</font>遇 龙 河-让人怦然心动的“小家碧玉”，因为它秀丽，清澈，鱼儿闲游，水筏飘摇<br><font color="#ff9703">7.</font>阳朔戏楼-秉承阳朔的独特的建设风格，世界第一大油纸伞，第一大铜鼓，第一大绣\n                    </div>\n                \n                \n                    \n                    \n                        \n                        \n                            <div class="detail-feature-photos">\n                                \n                                \n                                \n                                <div class="detail-feature-photo detail-feature-photo-2">\n                                    \n                                        \n                                            \n                                                <div class="detail-feature-photo-item">\n                                                    <div class="detail-feature-photo-item-inner">\n                                                        \n                                                            <img src="//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png" data-src="https://m.tuniucdn.com//fb2/t1/G2/M00/34/2D/Cii-Tli9e3eIH3nuAAVw77U-E30AAIIswLhVQMABXEH243_w450_h300_c1_t0.jpg">\n</div>\n                                                    \n                                                </div>\n                                            \n                                        